{"tid":1929006,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【股民熱話】神預測？2020年香港經濟差到「核爆」","createTime":"2020-03-16T16:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T17:12:50.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fce59edd11743a3e4535bbc050c35b723710637","tid":1929006,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"2019年11月04日 08:00<br />\n在中國人的角度，投資屬偏財，股民普遍都會「信邪」！每年中秋後就會出來年的「通書」(即「通勝」)，最近筆者就買了一本做定功課，睇完之後，對明年經濟前景有差到「核爆」的感覺！<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講？根據曆法，2019年是己亥豬年，而2020年是庚子鼠年。依「十二地支」，亥為一個周期最尾一年，而子則為一個新周期的開始。2019年香港面對內憂外患，經濟明顯轉差。老實講，自2007年到2019年這個周期，港府施政無甚建樹，土地政策一鑊粥，社會貧富懸殊日趨嚴重，金融及創新科技發展滯後，民生經濟都每況愈下，今年所出現的社會動盪，只是這些年不作為所累積的怨氣一次過爆發，可今年是周期之末，踏入明年開展的新周期，到底會是否極泰來，抑或沒有最差只有更差？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191104/bkn-20191104080057367-1104_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191104%2Fbkn-20191104080057367-1104_00842_001.html&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8J6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=ce31d1bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191104/bkn-20191104080057367-1104_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6822bde5af10c232661f23e349af05c1bb4924fe","tid":1929006,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c816c396e4f70fa9e22b17d155b72b1a89faa1d","tid":1929006,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}